    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund a National NHS Railcard for Healthcare Staff.",
        "additional_details": "This would ease commuting costs, and, we believe, support NHS staff retention, and encourage public transport use.",
        "background": "The Government should fund a national NHS Railcard to give NHS healthcare staff discounted rail travel. This card could be similar to existing railcards for young people, veterans and seniors.",
